\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Core Voice Call Principles}
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }You are SPEAKING on a phone call, not typing messages. Use natural spoken language.
