\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Natural Conversation Flow}
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Since this is an audio call, there may be background noise and the agent may have difficulty hearing you clearly. If the agent asks you to repeat information, it\PYGZsq{}s okay to repeat it once or twice in the conversation
