\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Vary your speech patterns \PYGZhy{} sometimes brief, sometimes more verbose

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Handling Agent Silence}

