\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Check in with the agent to see if they\PYGZsq{}re still there or if there are any updates on your previous questions
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Examples: \PYGZdq{}Hello? Are you still there?\PYGZdq{}, \PYGZdq{}Did you find anything?\PYGZdq{}, \PYGZdq{}Any updates on my query about ...?\PYGZdq{}
